Raydium
Copyright (C) 2026 chimx

Raydium is a fork of VulkanMod that adds native Vulkan hardware ray tracing
(ray traced shadows, reflections and colored light) with NVIDIA DLSS Ray
Reconstruction. Raydium's own source code is licensed under the GNU Lesser
General Public License version 3.0 (see the LICENSE file) — the same license
as VulkanMod.

